# Environment variables for local development
# Copy this file to .dev.vars and fill in your actual values
# Never commit .dev.vars to version control!

# Option A: Direct AI Provider Keys
# Get your API key from https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-your-key-here

# Optional: OpenAI API key
# Get your API key from https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-proj-your-key-here

# Option B: Cloudflare AI Gateway (Unified Billing)
# Use AI Gateway to route requests through Cloudflare for:
# - Unified billing (no provider API keys needed)
# - Request caching
# - Rate limiting
# - Analytics and monitoring
#
# Get these values from:
# https://dash.cloudflare.com/[account-id]/ai/ai-gateway
#
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=your-account-id
# CLOUDFLARE_GATEWAY_ID=your-gateway-id
# CLOUDFLARE_API_TOKEN=your-api-token
